  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Interventional study of the accuracy of a non-invasive testing by echocardiography to predict
      respiratory worsening after vascular filling.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Mitral Doppler will be performed before vascular filling. Patients will be classified in two
      groups (normal or high cardiac filling pressure).

      The evolution of the respiratory data (SpO2/FiO2) of the two groups of the patients before
      and after vascular filling will be compared.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
